            overview:`<div class="row setter"> <div class="overIntro"> <p class="ladakhIntro col-12 col-md-12">Embark on a transformative journey through Ladakh with our Cultural Immersion Holiday Package. This 7-day experience is crafted to connect travelers with the heart and soul of Ladakh, offering a unique opportunity to stay in local homes, engage with communities, and delve into the rich tapestry of Ladakhi heritage. From the majestic monasteries to the vibrant traditions of art, music, and cuisine, every moment is a chance to forge authentic connections and create lasting memories.</p> <h4 class="tripHitted col-md-12 col-12">Trip Highlights</h4> <div class="keyFeatures col-md-12 col-12"> <ul class="list-group"> <li class="list-group-item h-auto text-start ">Local Homestays: Immerse yourself in Ladakhi hospitality by staying with local families, gaining firsthand insights into their daily lives and cultural traditions.</li> <li class="list-group-item">Heritage Exploration: Uncover the secrets of Leh's ancient architecture, wander through the old town's narrow lanes, and marvel at the grandeur of monasteries like Shey, Hemis, and Thiksey.</li> <li class="list-group-item">Agricultural Experience: Connect with the land by participating in traditional farming activities. Share a meal with a farming family, tasting the organic bounty of Ladakh.</li> <li class="list-group-item">Culinary Delights: Indulge in Ladakhi cuisine with hands-on cooking classes, enjoying traditional meals with local hosts. Experience the flavors of the region through a carefully curated culinary journey.</li> <li class="list-group-item">Cultural Performances: Witness vibrant cultural performances, including traditional dances and music, bringing Ladakh's artistic heritage to life.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div>`,
